Currency Hedging and Risk Management: Showcase

What is this?

I got the idea for this project from my interest in finance and risk management and to brush up on my coding skills.

🔄 Exchange Rate Modeling

GARCH(1,1) Process

Volatility modeling using:

σ²ₜ = ω + α₁ε²ₜ₋₁ + β₁σ²ₜ₋₁

Where:

  • σ²ₜ: Conditional variance
  • ω: Long-term variance
  • α₁: ARCH parameter
  • β₁: GARCH parameter

💹 Hedging Strategies

1. Forward Rate Calculation

F = S × (1 + r_DKK)ᵗ / (1 + r_USD)ᵗ

Where:

  • F: Forward rate
  • S: Spot rate
  • r_DKK: Danish interest rate
  • r_USD: US interest rate
  • t: Time to maturity

2. Option Premium

Premium = N(d₁)S - N(d₂)Ke^(-rt)

Black-Scholes parameters:

  • d₁ = (ln(S/K) + (r + σ²/2)T) / (σ√T)
  • d₂ = d₁ - σ√T

📈 Risk Metrics

Value at Risk (VaR)

VaR₉₅% = μ - 1.645σ

Standard deviation calculation:

σ = √(Σ(x - μ)² / (n-1))

📊 Data Sources

  • USD/DKK Exchange Rates: Yahoo Finance (DKKUSD=X)
  • USD Interest Rates: Federal Reserve Economic Data (FRED)
  • DKK Interest Rates: Danmarks Nationalbank
